{
  "id": "5b90ad6c1280360014519cb5",
  "title": "エンジニアの知的生産術の幻の章",
  "created": 1536208244,
  "updated": 1644740394,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5b90ad6c1280360014519cb5",
      "text": "エンジニアの知的生産術の幻の章",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208244,
      "updated": 1536208858
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90ad74aff09e0000c9214e",
      "text": "[エンジニアの知的生産術]のp.165[(5.2.6.3) ふせんが膨大なときの表札作り]で、執筆の過程に",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208244,
      "updated": 1644740394
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90ae78aff09e0000c921a8",
      "text": ">この段階では「瞑想」という章がありましたが、あまりほかの章とうまくつながらないので削りました",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208504,
      "updated": 1536208508
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90ae66aff09e0000c921a6",
      "text": "と言う出来事があったと紹介されている。リポジトリを眺めていたら2017-04-10に見出し案から削除したテキストがコミットされていたので面白いからここに掲載しておく。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208487,
      "updated": 1536208609
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90b100aff09e0000c921f8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536209153,
      "updated": 1536209153
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90b100aff09e0000c921f9",
      "text": "この内容自体が「この本はどう作られたか」の章に入ると良さそう。 #エンジニアの知的生産術_加筆案",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536209153,
      "updated": 1644914379
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90b131aff09e0000c921fa",
      "text": "\t当初、この書籍が作られるプロセス自体の実データを付録の章などとして入れたらよいと考えてた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536209202,
      "updated": 1536218653
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90d61daff09e00002159e5",
      "text": " 削った現状でも割と本に厚みがあるので、編集者の入れないって判断は適切だった。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536218653,
      "updated": 1536218662
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90d627aff09e00002159e6",
      "text": " 増補版、紙の本ではなく電子で出す方が良いかも。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536218663,
      "updated": 1536218678
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90b022aff09e0000c921f6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208931,
      "updated": 1536208931
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90b022aff09e0000c921f7",
      "text": "「[瞑想]」の「[歯車の速度を落とす]」はp.204の「[辞書との照合]」のところで紹介している。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208931,
      "updated": 1636397010
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afbcaff09e0000c921f4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208829,
      "updated": 1536208829
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90aee7aff09e0000c921aa",
      "text": "元はMarkdownだったのだけどScrapboxに転載する際に箇条書きにしたほうがよいと思ったので`#`を■に置換した。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208615,
      "updated": 1536208891
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afc9aff09e0000c921f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208842,
      "updated": 1536208842
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90aee3aff09e0000c921a9",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208611,
      "updated": 1536208614
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ac",
      "text": "2017-04-10",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ad",
      "text": "第7章：つづけられない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ae",
      "text": " ■ 継続は目的？手段？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921af",
      "text": "\t 「つまみ食い勉強法」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b0",
      "text": " ■ 継続のために必要なもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b1",
      "text": "\t ■■ ハマるしかけ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b2",
      "text": "   ■■■ トリガー：きっかけが必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b3",
      "text": "   ■■■ リワード：報酬が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b4",
      "text": "   ■■■ インベストメント：投資が必要",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b5",
      "text": "\t ■■ 適切な難易度調整",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b6",
      "text": "\t\t ■■■ フロー理論：退屈と不安の狭間",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b8",
      "text": "第8章：片付かない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921b9",
      "text": "\t■ 「片付ける」とは？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ba",
      "text": "\t\tどこにあるかわかるようにすること。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921bb",
      "text": "  ■■ 分類",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921bc",
      "text": "\t  人間は最初から完璧な分類を作ることができない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921bd",
      "text": "  ■■ こうもり問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921be",
      "text": "  ■■ ポケットひとつ原則",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921bf",
      "text": "\t  分類を諦めて1か所にまとめる戦略",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c0",
      "text": " ■ 物と情報の違い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c1",
      "text": "  ■■ 場所の限定＝インデックス",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c2",
      "text": "\t  データベースのインデックスは「ここにはない」を効率よく判断できるようにすることで",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c3",
      "text": "\t\t  「どこにあるか」を見つける時間を削減するための仕組み",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536218715
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c5",
      "text": "   物理的なものの整理でも同じようにインデックスが機能する。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c6",
      "text": "\t   「領収書は全部この箱の中にある」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536218713
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c7",
      "text": "\t   他の場所にないと確信できることが効果発揮の要件。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536218714
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921c9",
      "text": "   ■■■ ボトムアップ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ca",
      "text": "\t   インデックスの作り方、ボトムアップに作る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921cb",
      "text": "   ■■■ 時間軸",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921cc",
      "text": "\t   時間軸は手軽なインデックス。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921cd",
      "text": "   ■■■ 検索",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ce",
      "text": "    物は検索しにくい。これを検索しやすくするアプローチ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921cf",
      "text": "    増井式超整理術、芋づる検索",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d0",
      "text": " ■ 混沌とクリエイティビティ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d1",
      "text": "  混沌はクリエイティビティを増すか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d2",
      "text": "  100枚の付箋を机に広げた「混沌」と、",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d3",
      "text": "  必要な道具を見つけることができない「混沌」は別物。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d4",
      "text": "  「混沌をして語らしめる」の川喜田二郎。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d6",
      "text": "第9章：焦燥感が強い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d7",
      "text": " ■ 理想と現実のギャップ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d8",
      "text": "  できること(現実)を超えた理想を目指すことで焦燥感が生まれる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921d9",
      "text": "  焦燥感は向上心のエンジンでもあるが、オーバーヒートして身を焼かない程度にコントロールが必要。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921da",
      "text": "  ■■ 完璧主義の問題",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921db",
      "text": "\t  最初から完璧を目指すことで苦しむ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921dc",
      "text": "  ■■ インクリメンタル",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921dd",
      "text": " \t 改善を繰り返し、徐々に良くしていく",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921de",
      "text": "  ■■ デフォルトゼロ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921df",
      "text": "   やらなければゼロなのだから何でもやってみよう",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e0",
      "text": "   失敗も学びの機会",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e1",
      "text": " ■ 身体性",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e2",
      "text": "\t (身体性という言葉は適切ではないかも、今はまだ代わりが思いつかない)",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e3",
      "text": "  やる気や焦燥感という「精神」に関する議論をする際に、「身体」を無関係なものとして無視してしまうのはおかしい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e4",
      "text": "  人間の精神は本人が思っている以上に、身体の影響を受けている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e5",
      "text": "  特に焦燥感に関しては、カフェインの摂取が影響することが知られている。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e6",
      "text": "\t ■■ カフェインに注意",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e7",
      "text": "   カフェインが焦燥感をもたらす",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e8",
      "text": "   緑茶のテアニンが焦燥感を緩和する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921e9",
      "text": "   カフェインとテアニンの両方を摂取する実験の紹介",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921ea",
      "text": "  ■■ 気温・水分・酸素・血糖値",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
    },
    {
      "id": "5b90afb7aff09e0000c921eb",
      "text": "  ■■ 頭痛",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1536208824,
      "updated": 1536208824
